===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  sodium_crypto_box_keypair(): string~

Generates a secret key and a public key as one string.

To get the secret key out of this unified keypair string, see 
|sodium_crypto_box_secretkey|. To get the public key out of this unified keypair
string, see |sodium_crypto_box_publickey|.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

This function has no parameters.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

One string containing both the X25519 secret key and corresponding X25519
public key.


